@startuml
actor User
participant "Orchestrator" as Orchestrator
participant "App" as App
participant "DB1" as DB1
participant "DB2" as DB2
participant "DB3" as DB3

== User request initiated ==

User -> Orchestrator: Request data

== Orchestrator handling parallel tasks ==

Orchestrator -> App: Call to fetch data (parallel)
App -> DB1: Fetch data (parallel)
App -> DB2: Fetch data (parallel)
App -> DB3: Fetch data (parallel)

== Fetch results from databases ==

DB1 --> App: Return data
DB2 --> App: Return data
DB3 --> App: Return data

App --> Orchestrator: Return merged data

== Return result to user ==

Orchestrator -> User: Return final data

@enduml
